review_blob: Mmmm.. Nui indeed! As someone who is slightly obsessed with truly BITTER beers, I wasnt too excited by the 80 IBU of this one. However, Ive been well and truly won over by the impressive lingering bitterness of this APA alongside the great combo of hop aromas and flavours over malts that are equal to the task of supporting all the awesomeness going on above.
